OL,3,CDisposable vapes to be banned in Wales
OL,4,Cthis weekend
OL,6,FDisposable vapes will be banned in
OL,7,FWales from this Sunday, June 1.
OL,9,FThe new law - which is in place across
OL,10,Fthe UK - will prohibit the sale of
OL,11,Fsingle use vapes.
OL,13,FThe law will be applied to businesses
OL,14,Fnot individuals, meaning that it will
OL,15,Fbe a criminal offence to sell or
OL,16,Fsupply disposable vapes but it will
OL,17,Fnot be illegal for people to use them
OL,18,Ffor personal use.
