OL,3,CDisposable vapes to be banned in Wales
OL,4,Cthis weekend
OL,6,FIt follows the soaring use of
OL,7,Fdisposable vapes in schools and a
OL,8,Fflood of plastic rubbish from the
OL,9,Fdiscarding of the devices.
OL,11,FDisposable vapes are non-refillable
OL,12,Fand unable to be recharged, and are
OL,13,Ftypically thrown away with general
OL,14,Fwaste in black bins or littered rather
OL,15,Fthan recycled.
OL,17,FEven when they are recycled, they need
OL,18,Fto be taken apart by hand, while their
OL,19,Fbatteries are a fire risk to recycling
OL,20,Ffacilities and can leak harmful
OL,21,Fchemicals into the environment.
