OL,3,CDisposable vapes to be banned in Wales
OL,4,Cthis weekend
OL,6,FRogue traders who continue to sell
OL,7,Fthem risk a fine of #200 in the first
OL,8,Finstance, followed by an unlimited
OL,9,Ffine or jail time for repeat offending.
OL,11,FPublic Health Wales has welcomed the
OL,12,Fban.
OL,14,FThe health body says that there is a
OL,15,F"clear consensus" among health experts
OL,16,Fthat the availability and marketing of
OL,17,Fdisposable vape products has driven a
OL,18,Fsignificant rise in vaping among
OL,19,Fchildren and young people.
