OL,3,CDisposable vapes to be banned in Wales
OL,4,Cthis weekend
OL,6,FThey say around 16% of year eleven
OL,7,Fpupils regularly use vapes and nearly
OL,8,Fhalf have tried vaping. Of these, most
OL,9,Fhad never smoked before taking up
OL,10,Fvaping.
OL,12,FWhile the majority of single-use vapes
OL,13,Fcontain nicotine, the ban will also
OL,14,Fapply to nicotine free disposable
OL,15,Fvapes.
OL,17,FAfter June 1, vapes will need to be
OL,18,Frefillable, rechargeable, and have a
OL,19,Freplaceable coil.
