OL,3,CDisposable vapes to be banned in Wales
OL,4,Cthis weekend
OL,6,FDeputy First Minister, with
OL,7,Fresponsibility for Climate Change, Huw
OL,8,FIrranca-Davies said: "Single-use vapes
OL,9,Fcreate litter and plastic pollution;
OL,10,Fthis ban will help stop the serious
OL,11,Fharm these products cause to our
OL,12,Fwildlife and environment.
OL,14,F"They should be recycled at a vape
OL,15,Fshop, or taken to a local authority
OL,16,Frecycling centre, to be disposed of
OL,17,Fsafely. Vapes should never go in the
OL,18,Fbin as they are susceptible to
OL,19,Fcatching fire."
