OL,3,CDisposable vapes to be banned in Wales
OL,4,Cthis weekend
OL,6,FMinister for Mental Health and
OL,7,FWellbeing, Sarah Murphy added: "In
OL,8,Faddition to the environmental impacts,
OL,9,Fwe know single-use vapes are being
OL,10,Fused by children and young people and
OL,11,Fare a factor in the significant
OL,12,Fincreases in youth vaping that we have
OL,13,Fseen in recent years.
OL,15,F"The single-use vape ban being
OL,16,Fintroduced will help us to protect
OL,17,Fchildren and young people from vape
OL,18,Fproducts so that they never start
OL,19,Fvaping and avoid the harms caused by
OL,20,Fnicotine addiction."
